# Malware Detection

## malfind

```bash
volatility -f memory.img --profile=Win7SP1x64 malfind
```

Purpose:

* Detects injected code or malicious memory regions

Signs of Malware:

* PAGE_EXECUTE_READWRITE
* Suspicious memory sections

---

# Extract Files from Memory

## dumpfiles

```bash
volatility -f memory.img --profile=Win7SP1x64 dumpfiles -D output/
```

Purpose:

* Extracts files from RAM

---

# Dump Process Memory

## procdump

```bash
volatility -f memory.img --profile=Win7SP1x64 procdump -p PID -D output/
```

Purpose:

* Dumps executable process memory

Example:

```bash
volatility -f memory.img --profile=Win7SP1x64 procdump -p 1234 -D output/
```

